com.eclipsesource.restfuse
Class DefaultCallbackResource

java.lang.Object
  com.eclipsesource.restfuse.CallbackResource
      com.eclipsesource.restfuse.DefaultCallbackResource

public class DefaultCallbackResource
extends CallbackResource

The DefaultCallbackResource is a default implementation for the CallbackResource which can be used within an http TestCase. All the methods return a default http response with the 204 (no content) response code.
